### Get existing note by ID (seeded in ENV=dev)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/notes/{{NOTE_ID}}
Accept: application/json

### Get note by non-existing ID (expected 404)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/notes/{{MISSING_NOTE_ID}}
Accept: application/json

### Get note with invalid ID format (expected 400)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/notes/not-a-number
Accept: application/json
